android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYS.description: Allows the application to mount and unmount file systems for removable storage.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.info: use the authentication credentials of an account

android.permission.REORDER_TASKS.description: Allows an application to move tasks to the foreground and background. Malicious applications can force themselves to the front without your control.

android.permission.ACCESS_NOTIFICATION_P.description: Marker permission for applications that wish to access notification policy.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

Built with option -pie.

playstore_details.title: Free Music - Unlimited offline Music download free
playstore_details.description:
Free Music Discover section shows you the hottest buzzing new music and artists daily, before anyone else. Discover, stream, and organize breaking new music now. 

Free Music - Unlimited Music offline player KEY FEATURES：
🎵Find new and trending new music first. Be the first of your friends to be up on what’s next.
🎵Unlimited streaming and music - play as much Hip-Hop, Electronic, Latin, Reggae, Pop, and Afropop as you want.
🎵 Listen to Free Online Music from YouTube，Discover New & Trending music, automatically personalized according to your preference.
🎵Create infinite playlists and organize your music
🎵Enjoy the gorgeous and modern design

UNLIMITED FREE MUSIC：
🎵Enjoy millions of free up-to-date songs form Youtube Music.
🎵Multitasking while listening to music using the Floating Player
🎵use it with headphones and speakers!
🎵Music is displayed and can be controlled on the screen. So you can enjoy music while using other apps.
🎵Full featured in app media player: repeat one/all, shuffle.

DISCLAIMER
Free Music Player is a legal and compliant 3rd-party API client that lets you play music & videos from YouTube & MP3s all within one app. (This is NOT an MP3 / video downloader app)
